Might be. The ETA is definitely off by one.

Here is the small script I used to test this:

``` python
import time

import click

@click.command()
@click.option('--count', default=1)
def test(count):
    with click.progressbar(range(count)) as bar:
        for x in bar:
            time.sleep(2)

if __name__ == '__main__':
    test()
```
